---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: About
seo:
  title: About Vandore Heritage
  description: Meet the team curating heritage properties, refined rentals, and relocation journeys across Latvia.
_enabled_editors:
  - visual
  - data
hero:
  eyebrow: About Vandore Heritage
  headline: A studio agency built on stewardship
  subheadline: We are a multidisciplinary team of strategists, restorers, and hospitality specialists who deliver property experiences with care.
  cta_label: Meet our team
  cta_url: /team/
values:
  heading: What guides every mandate
  items:
    - title: Stewardship first
      description: We handle every property as a living narrative, balancing commercial outcomes with respect for the people and history involved.
    - title: Precision with warmth
      description: From due diligence to handovers, our processes are rigorous while remaining calm, human, and reassuring.
    - title: Radical transparency
      description: Weekly briefings, open pipelines, and candid advice keep owners and tenants in control of every decision.
team_intro:
  heading: Your core partners
  description: A nimble team supported by a trusted network of conservators, legal specialists, and hospitality experts.
team:
  - name: Laura Vandore
    role: Founder & Lead Strategist
    bio: 15 years guiding heritage transactions and complex relocations across the Baltics.
  - name: Martins Ozols
    role: Head of Client Experience
    bio: Hospitality executive ensuring every brief feels orchestrated.
  - name: Ieva Kravale
    role: Conservation Partnerships
    bio: Architectural historian connecting restorers with the right artisans.
---
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.eyebrow">{{ hero.eyebrow }}</p>
    <h1 data-cms-bind="#hero.headline">{{ hero.headline }}</h1>
    <p data-cms-bind="#hero.subheadline">{{ hero.subheadline }}</p>
    <a class="cta" href="{{ hero.cta_url }}"><span data-cms-bind="#hero.cta_label">{{ hero.cta_label }}</span></a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 data-cms-bind="#values.heading">{{ values.heading }}</h2>
    <div class="grid two">
      {% for value in values.items %}
      <article class="card" data-cms-collection="values" data-cms-item="{{ loop.index0 }}">
        <h3 data-cms-bind="title">{{ value.title }}</h3>
        <p data-cms-bind="description">{{ value.description }}</p>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section alt">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 data-cms-bind="#team_intro.heading">{{ team_intro.heading }}</h2>
    <p data-cms-bind="#team_intro.description">{{ team_intro.description }}</p>
    <div class="grid two">
      {% for person in team %}
      <article class="card" data-cms-collection="team" data-cms-item="{{ loop.index0 }}">
        <h3 data-cms-bind="name">{{ person.name }}</h3>
        <p class="meta" data-cms-bind="role">{{ person.role }}</p>
        <p data-cms-bind="bio">{{ person.bio }}</p>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

